;
SHEET
DETERMINATION METHOD: DSSP
THE SHEETS PRESENTED AS "BA" IN EACH CHAIN ON SHEET RECORDS
BELOW IS ACTUALLY AN 11-STRANDED BARREL THIS IS REPRESENTED BY
A 12-STRANDED SHEET IN WHICH THE FIRST AND LAST STRANDS
ARE IDENTICAL.
;
